# Quick Reference

| Command | Description |
|----------|----------|
| `chmod u=rwx file` | User full access |
| `chmod g=r file` | Group read only |
| `chmod o=rw file` | Others read and write |
| `chmod o=` file | Remove all permissions from others |
| `chmod +x file` | Add execute permission |
| `chmod -x file` | Remove execute permission |
| `chmod 755 file` | Common executable permission |
| `chmod 644 file` | Common file permission |
| `./file.sh` | Execute file |
